name: Tim Walz
email: info@tinaforminnesota.com
subject: Let’s leave it all out on the field
body: Folks, this is Tim Walz. I couldn't be prouder to be on this ticket and tohelp make Kamala Harris the next president of the United States. There’s a lotmore I want to say, but before I continue, I’m hoping you’ll split acontribution between Tina Smith and our campaign today. With just four daysleft in this election, we need to leave it all out on the field. Everycontribution will make a huge difference.[https://secure.actblue.com/donate/tsm-em-harris24?email=dpwillis67@gmail.com]If you've saved your payment information with ActBlue Express, your splitdonation to Tina Smith and the Harris-Walz campaign will go throughimmediately: CHIP IN $10 NOW [https://secure.actblue.com/donate/tsm-em-harris24?express_lane=true&amount;=10&email;=dpwillis67@gmail.com] CHIP IN $25NOW [https://secure.actblue.com/donate/tsm-em-harris24?express_lane=true&amount;=25&email;=dpwillis67@gmail.com] CHIP IN $50NOW [https://secure.actblue.com/donate/tsm-em-harris24?express_lane=true&amount;=50&email;=dpwillis67@gmail.com] CHIP IN$100 NOW [https://secure.actblue.com/donate/tsm-em-harris24?express_lane=true&amount;=100&email;=dpwillis67@gmail.com] CHIP IN$250 NOW [https://secure.actblue.com/donate/tsm-em-harris24?express_lane=true&amount;=250&email;=dpwillis67@gmail.com] ANOTHERAMOUNT [https://secure.actblue.com/donate/tsm-em-harris24?email=dpwillis67@gmail.com] Growing up in a small town like Butte,Nebraska, you learn to take care of each other. The family down the road maynot think, pray, or love like you, but they are your neighbors and you lookout for them. Now we know that Donald Trump, JD Vance, and MAGA Republicanshave a different vision of America. When they talk about freedom they mean thegovernment should have the freedom to invade every corner of our life. Take itfrom a small-town guy: they know nothing about what working people need.That's not what we do in Minnesota. We don’t attack our neighbors’ rights. Wewelcome everyone in, and we lift each other up. My friend Tina Smithunderstands this. And she works hard every day to ensure Minnesotans’ voicesare heard in the United States Senate. That’s what this campaign is about:working together to build a future where everyone has the opportunity not justto get by, but to get ahead. Where workers come first, health care and housingare human rights, and the government stays the hell out of your bedroom. Butwe need you in this fight with us. Will you split a donation of $10, orwhatever works for you right now, between Tina Smith and our campaign so wecan continue working together and defend our values up and down the ballot inNovember? [https://secure.actblue.com/donate/tsm-em-harris24?email=dpwillis67@gmail.com&amount;=10] Four days to go. Let’s leaveit all on the field.
